https://filmhafizasi.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/martinscorseseafp-652e9dc5d4744865431626-768x432.jpg 768w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px&quot; data-pin-no-hover=&quot;true&quot; style=&quot;height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 5px auto 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; clear: both; text-align: center; display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;cf-tweet-this cf-tt-target cf-tt-out-of-bounds cf-tt-out-of-bounds-bottom cf-tt-element-attached-center cf-tt-target-attached-center cf-tt-enabled cf-tt-element-attached-bottom cf-tt-target-attached-top cf-tt-abutted cf-tt-abutted-top&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Lora, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;Geçtiğimiz sene&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;73. Berlin Film Festivali’nde&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;aynı ödülün sahibi&amp;nbsp;&lt;em style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Fabelmans&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;filmini de festivalde tanıtan&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Steven Spielberg&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;olmuştu.&amp;nbsp;15-25 Şubat 2024 tarihleri arasında yapılması planlanan bir sonraki Berlin Film Festivali ise bu kez&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Martin Scorsese&lt;/span&gt;’in yaşam boyu başarısını ödüllendirecek.&amp;nbsp;&lt;em style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;“Sinemayı hem kişisel hem evrensel bir şekilde bir hikayeyi şekillendirme sanatı olarak gören herkes için Martin Scorsese eşsiz bir model.”&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;şeklinde konuşan festival direktörleri,&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Scorsese’&lt;/span&gt;in filmlerinin tarihe eşlik ettiğini de ekledi.&amp;nbsp;&lt;em style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;“Onun tarih ve insanlığa bakış açısı içimizde kim olduğumuzu ve nereden geldiğimizi anlamamıza ve sorgulamamıza yardımcı oldu. Son filmi Killers of the Flower Moon onun en büyük başarılarından biri.”&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;ifadelerini kullandı.&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Berlinale Special&lt;/span&gt;’ın ev sahipliği yapacağı filmler arasında&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Julia von Heinz’dan&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Treasure,&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Tilman Singer’&lt;/span&gt;dan&amp;nbsp;&lt;em style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Cuckoo&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;ve&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Tsai Ming-liang&lt;/span&gt;’dan&amp;nbsp;&lt;em style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Abiding Nowhere&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;yer alacak. Bunun yanısıra&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Amanda Seyfried, Lena Dunham,&amp;nbsp;Stephen Fry, Riley Keough, Jesse Eisenberg, Hunter Schafer&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;ve&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Dan Stevens&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;gibi isimler de festivalde gösterilecek filmlerin oyuncu kadrosunda yer alıyor. Festival programının tamamı Ocak ortasında açıklanacak.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;74. Berlin Film Festivali’&lt;/span&gt;nin jüri başkanı ise Kenya’lı oyuncu&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Lupita Nyong’o&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;olacak.&lt;/p&gt;');

